The first - create service

In the Linux start create_server.py

command:
$ nohup create_server.py &

In the Windows running create_client.py, then input in the GUI

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

The second - manage service

In the Linux start manage_server.py

command:
$ nohup manage_server.py &

In the Windows running manage_client.py, then choice the servername of you want to manage.



